  - SetUnitAnimation (var:gg_unit_nfor_0612, const:attack)
  - SetUnitAnimation (var:gg_unit_ndqn_0615, const:death)
  - PolledWait (const:2.00)
  - CreateTextTagUnitBJ (const:|cFFFFFF99没有足够的能力，等待你的将会是无尽的后悔！|r, var:gg_unit_nfor_0612, const:80.00, const:10, const:100.00, const:100.00, const:100.00, const:0)
